OL,3,CBig Issue founder steps up anti-
OL,4,Cpoverty campaign
OL,6,FThe founder of the Big Issue magazine
OL,7,Fis taking action in Parliament aimed
OL,8,Fat persuading the government to do
OL,9,Fmore to fight rising levels of poverty.
OL,11,FLord John Bird has tabled an amendment
OL,12,Fto the Children's Wellbeing and
OL,13,FSchools Bill, and is warning that
OL,14,FLabour will not hold back the rise of
OL,15,FReform UK at the next general election
OL,16,Funless it acts now.
