OL,3,CBig Issue founder steps up anti-
OL,4,Cpoverty campaign
OL,6,FLord Bird has proposed a new clause to
OL,7,Fthe Bill, which is currently being
OL,8,Fprepared for scrutiny at committee
OL,9,Fstage in the House of Lords, which
OL,10,Fwould place a new duty on the
OL,11,Fgovernment to set targets for the
OL,12,Freduction of child poverty.
OL,14,FThe move comes as a survey of more
OL,15,Fthan 2,000 adults for the Big Issue
OL,16,Ffound that seven out of 10 believed
OL,17,FLabour should be doing more in their
OL,18,Fapproach to poverty.
