OL,4,Cpoverty campaign
OL,6,FPublic disapproval on the issue has
OL,7,Frisen by 18% in the past six months,
OL,8,Fsaid the Big Issue.
OL,10,FThe magazine is campaigning for a
OL,11,Fwider 'Poverty Zero' law ` the
OL,12,Festablishment of statutory poverty
OL,13,Freduction targets, similar to net zero.
OL,15,FLord John Bird said: "As the local
OL,16,Felections showed, the big question for
OL,17,FLabour now is how to stop a mass
OL,18,Fexodus of its supporters defecting to
OL,19,Ftheir rivals.
