OL,3,CBig Issue founder steps up anti-
OL,4,Cpoverty campaign
OL,6,F"That's no easy task when so many
OL,7,Fissues divide the British public, but
OL,8,Fas our poll shows, on one issue they
OL,9,Fare united ` there must be more done
OL,10,Ffor the 14 million people in poverty
OL,11,Fin this country.
OL,13,F"My amendment to the Children's
OL,14,FWellbeing and Schools Bill would mean
OL,15,Fall future governments will be held to
OL,16,Faccount on reducing child poverty.
