OL,3,CBig Issue founder steps up anti-
OL,4,Cpoverty campaign
OL,6,F"It would hold this Government's feet
OL,7,Fto the fire in taking long-term, truly
OL,8,Fpreventative action for the 4.3
OL,9,Fmillion children in this country who
OL,10,Fcurrently live in poverty, and signal
OL,11,Fto the UK public that they are finally
OL,12,Ftaking poverty seriously."
OL,14,FA Government spokesperson said: "No
OL,15,Fchild should be living in poverty,
OL,16,Fwhich is why we have already taken
OL,17,Fwide-ranging action to break the
OL,18,Funfair link between background and
OL,19,Fopportunity, led by our cross-
OL,20,Fgovernment child poverty taskforce.
